<span id="freeTextContainer18197232026943181013">I was disappointed. The jacket review and indeed the title of the book allude to the focus of the story being about a mystery surrounding the letters stored in the hatboxes. I got to chapter 5 and wondered when the story was going to start. The book did mention the letters but with no more consequence than if it was describing the birds singing after a morning shower. It was too boring to continue reading.</span>

